ar check-ins or virtual coffee breaks. Staying connected reduces feelings of isolation and supports collaboration.\\n\\n8. **Leverage Communication Tools Effectively**  \\n   *Tip:* Use chat apps for quick questions and video calls for more complex discussions. Clear, appropriate communication saves time and prevents misunderstandings.\\n\\n9. **Set Boundaries with Housemates or Family**  \\n   *Tip:* Communicate your work hours and workspace to others at home and use visual cues (like headphones or a closed door) to indicate when you shouldn\u2019t be disturbed.\\n\\n10. **Regularly Review and Adjust Your Workflow**  \\n    *Tip:* Each week, reflect on what\u2019s working and what could improve. Adapt tools, routines, or environments as needed to stay productive and satisfied.\\n\\nThese strategies, supported by research and effectiveness analysis, can help remote workers of all backgrounds maintain high productivity and well-being.', name=None, tool_call_id=None, tool_calls=None, audio=None, images=None, videos=None, files=None, audio_output=None, image_output=None, thinking=None, redacted_thinking=None, provider_data=None, citations=None, reasoning_content=None, tool_name=None, tool_args=None, tool_call_error=None, stop_after_tool_call=False, add_to_agent_memory=True, from_history=False, metrics=MessageMetrics(input_tokens=160, output_tokens=477, total_tokens=637, audio_tokens=0, input_audio_tokens=0, output_audio_tokens=0, cached_tokens=0, cache_write_tokens=0, reasoning_tokens=0, prompt_tokens=160, completion_tokens=477, prompt_tokens_details={'audio_tokens': 0, 'cached_tokens': 0}, completion_tokens_details={'accepted_prediction_tokens': 0, 'audio_tokens': 0, 'reasoning_tokens': 0, 'rejected_prediction_tokens': 0}, additional_metrics=None, time=7.048953291960061, time_to_first_token=None, timer=<agno.utils.timer.Timer object at 0x117c28190>), references=None, created_at=1755732925)], metrics={'input_tokens': [160], 'output_tokens': [477], 'total_tokens': [637]